'''Drallish crowns''' were units of currency on the planet [[Drall (planet)|Drall]]. The tutor [[Ebrihim]] paid 1150 Drallish crowns to purchase the experimental droid [[Q9-X2]], although the sales receipt showed the droid cost 1250 crowns.

